    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. While the engine and transmission are functional, the car shows clear signs of its age, including several noticeable scratches and a small dent on the rear passenger door. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and the driver's seat shows significant wear. Mechanically, it runs and drives, but it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It\u2019s an honest car for someone looking for a budget-friendly option that needs some TLC.",
